            <p>Nintendo has announced a Direct focused exclusively on its upcoming <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/movies/the-super-mario-galaxy-movie-2026">The Super Mario Galaxy Movie</a>.</p>
<p>The Direct itself will feature the world premiere of The Super Mario Galaxy Movie trailer and take place tomorrow, 12th November, at 2pm UK time. For our friends across the pond, that's 6am PT / 9am ET.</p>
